{"tid":2066342,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陶傑：北京肺炎爆發！北京往洛磯山航班又爆滿！","createTime":"2020-06-16T08:26:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T08:54:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aca0d34cb1bc7e4cb82c881389ca7e5caeb95968","tid":2066342,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/nrKPQLwH/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FnrKPQLwH%2Fimage.jpg&h=81654f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報這是昨天北京飛洛杉磯的航班，都有美國綠卡。<br />\n<br />\n在班次限制的情況下，飛美國的航機是班班客滿。<br />\n<br />\n當初武漢疫情爆發，這群人馬上從中國跑到美國。<br />\n<br />\n後來美國疫情控制不住了，這群人又從美國跑回中國。<br />\n<br />\n現在北京爆出來疫情，他們又從北京再次跑回美國。<br />\n<br />\n都是同一群人。你們累不累啊？<br />\n<br />\n只要美國那邊千萬不要將居留權給「制裁」掉，就不累。"},{"pid":"21215334174cc989aefb5c9bf49a1b6f845189c6","tid":2066342,"uid":139173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:28:36.000Z","msg":"中國人入境美國已經係對美國最大制裁<br />\n中國點會輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5767b8d49625328dbc6c980bb98fb136eafc667c","tid":2066342,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:36:15.000Z","msg":"tweet咗畀契爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎rt<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sparda61362019/status/1272809949748494336?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsparda61362019%2Fstatus%2F1272809949748494336%3Fs%3D09&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aaxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=c33096d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsparda61362019%2Fstatus%2F1272809949748494336%3Fs%3D09&h=b5b78315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sparda61362019/status/1272809949748494336?s=09</a>"},{"pid":"cc5a23d